PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773843068
OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FIsrael launched a new "wide-scale wave
OL,8,Fof strikes" across Iran's capital on
OL,9,FTuesday and stepped up attacks on Iran-
OL,10,Fbacked Hezbollah militants in Lebanon
OL,11,Fas Tehran retaliated with strikes that
OL,12,Ftargeted the US embassy in Iraq.
OL,14,FThe US embassy in Baghdad was
OL,15,Freportedly damaged when it was hit
OL,16,Fwith shrapnel from drones launched by
OL,17,FIran-linked proxy forces that had been
OL,18,Fintercepted. A two-minute video posted
OL,19,Fon Telegram by a pro-Iranian militia
OL,20,Fappeared to show a drone flying over
OL,21,Fthe US Embassy compound in Baghdad.
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773843068
OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FIran also continued attacks on Gulf
OL,8,Fstates, prompting the brief closure of
OL,9,Fairspace in the United Arab Emirates
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,12,FThe Israeli military said its attacks
OL,13,Facross Tehran and the Lebanese capital
OL,14,Fon Tuesday morning were targeting
OL,15,FHezbollah militants.
OL,17,FSome Israeli troops have pushed into
OL,18,Fsouthern Lebanon, and there are fears
OL,19,FIsrael is preparing a large-scale
OL,20,Finvasion despite calls from some
OL,21,FWestern leaders to de-escalate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
