OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FStrikes on Gulf States
OL,9,FThe United Arab Emirates briefly shut
OL,10,Fits airspace on Tuesday as the
OL,11,Fmilitary said it was "responding to
OL,12,Fincoming missile and drone threats".
OL,14,FThe closure was soon lifted, and not
OL,15,Flong after, shortly after, explosions
OL,16,Fwere heard as air defences intercepted
OL,17,Fincoming fire
OL,26,@sD@VOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
