OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FSaudi Arabia's Defence Ministry
OL,8,Freported intercepting a dozen drones
OL,9,FTuesday morning over the country's
OL,10,Fvast Eastern Province, home to oil
OL,11,Finfrastructure.
OL,13,FIn Qatar, the sounds of explosions
OL,14,Fwere heard over the capital early in
OL,15,Fthe day as defences worked to
OL,16,Fintercept incoming fire. Qatar's
OL,17,FDefence Ministry said later that it
OL,18,Fhad successfully thwarted a missile
OL,19,Fattack on the city, though a fire
OL,20,Fbroke out in an industrial area from a
OL,21,Fdowned projectile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
