PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773843068
OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FThe US embassy in Iraq was hit with
OL,8,Fshrapnel on Tuesday after air defences
OL,9,Fwere able to shoot down all four
OL,10,Fdrones targeting the facility.
OL,12,FA separate strike targeted a house in
OL,13,Fthe heavily fortified Presidential
OL,14,FCompound in Baghdad's al-Jadriya area,
OL,15,Fofficials said. It wasn't clear who
OL,16,Fcarried out either attack, but Iran-
OL,17,Fallied militias have regularly been
OL,18,Fattacking American targets inside Iraq
OL,19,Fsince the conflict began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
