OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FSome Israeli troops have pushed into
OL,8,Fsouthern Lebanon, and there are fears
OL,9,FIsrael is preparing a large-scale
OL,10,Finvasion.
OL,12,FThe military's chief of staff, Lt.
OL,13,FGen. Eyal Zamir, said Monday on a
OL,14,Fvisit to the northern border that
OL,15,FIsrael's army is "determined to deepen
OL,16,Fthe operation until all of our
OL,17,Fobjectives are achieved" and that the
OL,18,Fmilitary's Northern Command is being
OL,19,Freinforced with additional soldiers.
OL,26,@wD@ROUyD@XO]
