OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FIsrael reported two Iranian attacks
OL,8,Fearly on Tuesday fired toward Tel Aviv
OL,9,Fand an area south of the Sea of
OL,10,FGalilee. Additional rocket launches
OL,11,Ffrom Lebanon were also reported.
OL,13,FTrump demands allies help protect
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz
OL,16,FTrump has called for countries,
OL,17,Fincluding the UK, to join a mission to
OL,18,Fprotect shipping in the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz, but the PM has so far resisted
OL,20,Fthe US president's demands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
