OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FIran has effectively shut the vital
OL,8,Foil and gas shipping route by
OL,9,Ftargeting vessels in response to the
OL,10,FUS-Israeli air strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
