PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773843068
OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FThere have been a handful of ships
OL,8,Fgetting through, primarily Iranian but
OL,9,Falso from other countries including
OL,10,FIndia and Turkey, and Iranian Foreign
OL,11,FMinister Abbas Araghchi said that
OL,12,F"from our perspective it is open"
OL,13,F`though Iranian officials say the
OL,14,Froute remains closed to the United
OL,15,FStates, Israel and their allies. A
OL,16,Ftanker anchored off the eastern coast
OL,17,Fof the United Arab Emirates was hit by
OL,18,Fa projectile early on Tuesday morning.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
