PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773843068
OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FThe closure of the Strait has seen the
OL,8,Fprice of crude oil soar, with a barrel
OL,9,Fnow costing more than $100.
OL,11,FThe increase has seen Starmer pledge
OL,12,F#53 million of support to ease the
OL,13,Fcost of living pressures in the UK,
OL,14,Ftargeted at customers who are "most
OL,15,Fexposed" to the consequences of rising
OL,16,Foil and gas prices, including those
OL,17,Fwho rely on heating oil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
