PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773843068
OL,3,CUS Embassy in Baghdad targeted as
OL,4,CIsrael launches 'wide-scale' strikes
OL,5,Con Iran
OL,7,FUS allies have largely resisted US
OL,8,Fpresident Donald Trump calls to send
OL,9,Fwarships. Europeans have been critical
OL,10,Fof the US and Israel for failing to
OL,11,Fprovide clarity on their objectives in
OL,12,Fthe war and have suggested that they
OL,13,Fare more interested in a diplomatic
OL,14,Fsolution than getting dragged into the
OL,15,Fconflict.
OL,17,FSo far, Germany, Spain, Italy, Japan
OL,18,Fand Australia have ruled out sending
OL,19,Fvessels to the strait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
